{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.1","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 24:1","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.023.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.024.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Joas, roi de Juda. Le temple r\u00e9par\u00e9<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-16: cf. 2 R 12:1-16. Ps 69:10.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.24.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Joas avait sept ans lorsqu\u2019il devint roi, et il r\u00e9gna quarante ans \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem. Sa m\u00e8re s\u2019appelait Tsibja, de Beer-Sch\u00e9ba.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24","name":"2 Chroniques 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.2","name":"2 Chroniques 24:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.23.21","name":"2 Chroniques 23:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.23.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.2","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 24:2","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.024.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.024.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.24.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Joas fit ce qui est droit aux yeux de l\u2019\u00c9ternel pendant toute la vie du sacrificateur Jehojada.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24","name":"2 Chroniques 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.3","name":"2 Chroniques 24:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.1","name":"2 Chroniques 24:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.3","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 24:3","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.024.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.024.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.24.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Jehojada prit pour Joas deux femmes, et Joas engendra des fils et des filles.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24","name":"2 Chroniques 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.4","name":"2 Chroniques 24:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.2","name":"2 Chroniques 24:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.4","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 24:4","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.024.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.024.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.24.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Apr\u00e8s cela, Joas eut la pens\u00e9e de r\u00e9parer la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24","name":"2 Chroniques 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.5","name":"2 Chroniques 24:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.3","name":"2 Chroniques 24:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.5","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 24:5","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.024.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.024.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.24.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Il assembla les sacrificateurs et les L\u00e9vites, et leur dit: Allez par les villes de Juda, et vous recueillerez dans tout Isra\u00ebl de l\u2019argent, chaque ann\u00e9e, pour r\u00e9parer la maison de votre Dieu; et mettez \u00e0 cette affaire de l\u2019empressement. Mais les L\u00e9vites ne se h\u00e2t\u00e8rent point.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24","name":"2 Chroniques 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.6","name":"2 Chroniques 24:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.4","name":"2 Chroniques 24:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.6","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 24:6","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.024.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.024.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.24.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Le roi appela Jehojada, le souverain sacrificateur, et lui dit: Pourquoi n\u2019as-tu pas veill\u00e9 \u00e0 ce que les L\u00e9vites apportassent de Juda et de J\u00e9rusalem l\u2019imp\u00f4t ordonn\u00e9 par Mo\u00efse, serviteur de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, et mis sur l\u2019assembl\u00e9e d\u2019Isra\u00ebl pour la tente du t\u00e9moignage?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24","name":"2 Chroniques 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.7","name":"2 Chroniques 24:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.5","name":"2 Chroniques 24:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.7","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 24:7","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.024.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.024.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.24.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Car l\u2019impie Athalie et ses fils ont ravag\u00e9 la maison de Dieu et fait servir pour les Baals toutes les choses consacr\u00e9es \u00e0 la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24","name":"2 Chroniques 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.8","name":"2 Chroniques 24:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.6","name":"2 Chroniques 24:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.8","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 24:8","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.024.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.024.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.24.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Alors le roi ordonna qu\u2019on f\u00eet un coffre, et qu\u2019on le pla\u00e7\u00e2t \u00e0 la porte de la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, en dehors.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24","name":"2 Chroniques 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.9","name":"2 Chroniques 24:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.7","name":"2 Chroniques 24:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.9","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 24:9","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.024.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.024.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.24.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Et l\u2019on publia dans Juda et dans J\u00e9rusalem qu\u2019on apport\u00e2t \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel l\u2019imp\u00f4t mis par Mo\u00efse, serviteur de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, sur Isra\u00ebl dans le d\u00e9sert.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24","name":"2 Chroniques 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.10","name":"2 Chroniques 24:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.8","name":"2 Chroniques 24:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.10","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 24:10","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.024.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.024.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.24.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Tous les chefs et tout le peuple s\u2019en r\u00e9jouirent, et l\u2019on apporta et jeta dans le coffre tout ce qu\u2019on avait \u00e0 payer.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24","name":"2 Chroniques 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.11","name":"2 Chroniques 24:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.9","name":"2 Chroniques 24:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.11","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 24:11","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.024.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.024.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.24.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Quand c\u2019\u00e9tait le moment o\u00f9 les L\u00e9vites, voyant qu\u2019il y avait beaucoup d\u2019argent dans le coffre, devaient le livrer aux inspecteurs royaux, le secr\u00e9taire du roi et le commissaire du souverain sacrificateur venaient vider le coffre; ils le prenaient et le remettaient \u00e0 sa place; ils faisaient ainsi journellement, et ils recueillirent de l\u2019argent en abondance.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24","name":"2 Chroniques 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.12","name":"2 Chroniques 24:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.10","name":"2 Chroniques 24:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.12","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 24:12","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.024.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.024.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.24.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Le roi et Jehojada le donnaient \u00e0 ceux qui \u00e9taient charg\u00e9s de faire ex\u00e9cuter l\u2019ouvrage dans la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, et qui prenaient \u00e0 gage des tailleurs de pierres et des charpentiers pour r\u00e9parer la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, et aussi des ouvriers en fer ou en airain pour r\u00e9parer la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24","name":"2 Chroniques 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.13","name":"2 Chroniques 24:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.11","name":"2 Chroniques 24:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.13","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 24:13","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.024.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.024.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.24.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Ceux qui \u00e9taient charg\u00e9s de l\u2019ouvrage travaill\u00e8rent, et les r\u00e9parations s\u2019ex\u00e9cut\u00e8rent par leurs soins; ils remirent en \u00e9tat la maison de Dieu et la consolid\u00e8rent.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24","name":"2 Chroniques 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.14","name":"2 Chroniques 24:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.12","name":"2 Chroniques 24:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.14","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 24:14","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.024.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.024.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.24.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Lorsqu\u2019ils eurent achev\u00e9, ils apport\u00e8rent devant le roi et devant Jehojada le reste de l\u2019argent; et l\u2019on en fit des ustensiles pour la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, des ustensiles pour le service et pour les holocaustes, des coupes, et d\u2019autres ustensiles d\u2019or et d\u2019argent. Et, pendant toute la vie de Jehojada, on offrit continuellement des holocaustes dans la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24","name":"2 Chroniques 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.15","name":"2 Chroniques 24:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.13","name":"2 Chroniques 24:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.15","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 24:15","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.024.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.024.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.24.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Jehojada mourut, \u00e2g\u00e9 et rassasi\u00e9 de jours; il avait \u00e0 sa mort cent trente ans.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24","name":"2 Chroniques 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.16","name":"2 Chroniques 24:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.14","name":"2 Chroniques 24:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.16","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 24:16","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.024.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.024.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.24.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>On l\u2019enterra dans la ville de David avec les rois, parce qu\u2019il avait fait du bien en Isra\u00ebl, et \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9gard de Dieu et \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9gard de sa maison.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24","name":"2 Chroniques 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.17","name":"2 Chroniques 24:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.15","name":"2 Chroniques 24:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.17","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 24:17","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.024.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.024.018,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Retour \u00e0 l\u2019idol\u00e2trie; Zacharie, fils du souverain sacrificateur, lapid\u00e9 par ordre du roi. \u2014 Invasion des Syriens. Joas assassin\u00e9<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 17-27: cf. 2 R 12:17-21. Mt 23:35. (Ga 5:7. Ap 3:11.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.24.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Apr\u00e8s la mort de Jehojada, les chefs de Juda vinrent se prosterner devant le roi. Alors le roi les \u00e9couta.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24","name":"2 Chroniques 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.18","name":"2 Chroniques 24:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.16","name":"2 Chroniques 24:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.18","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 24:18","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.024.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.024.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.24.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Et ils abandonn\u00e8rent la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu de leurs p\u00e8res, et ils servirent les Astart\u00e9s et les idoles. La col\u00e8re de l\u2019\u00c9ternel fut sur Juda et sur J\u00e9rusalem, parce qu\u2019ils s\u2019\u00e9taient ainsi rendus coupables.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24","name":"2 Chroniques 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.19","name":"2 Chroniques 24:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.17","name":"2 Chroniques 24:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.19","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 24:19","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.024.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.024.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.24.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel envoya parmi eux des proph\u00e8tes pour les ramener \u00e0 lui, mais ils n\u2019\u00e9cout\u00e8rent point les avertissements qu\u2019ils en re\u00e7urent.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24","name":"2 Chroniques 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.20","name":"2 Chroniques 24:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.18","name":"2 Chroniques 24:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.20","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 24:20","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.024.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.024.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.24.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Zacharie, fils du sacrificateur Jehojada, fut rev\u00eatu de l\u2019esprit de Dieu; il se pr\u00e9senta devant le peuple et lui dit: Ainsi parle Dieu: Pourquoi transgressez-vous les commandements de l\u2019\u00c9ternel? Vous ne prosp\u00e9rerez point; car vous avez abandonn\u00e9 l\u2019\u00c9ternel, et il vous abandonnera.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24","name":"2 Chroniques 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.21","name":"2 Chroniques 24:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.19","name":"2 Chroniques 24:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.21","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 24:21","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.024.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.024.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.24.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Et ils conspir\u00e8rent contre lui, et le lapid\u00e8rent par ordre du roi, dans le parvis de la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24","name":"2 Chroniques 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.22","name":"2 Chroniques 24:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.20","name":"2 Chroniques 24:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.22","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 24:22","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.024.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.024.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.24.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Le roi Joas ne se souvint pas de la bienveillance qu\u2019avait eue pour lui Jehojada, p\u00e8re de Zacharie, et il fit p\u00e9rir son fils. Zacharie dit en mourant: Que l\u2019\u00c9ternel voie, et qu\u2019il fasse justice!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24","name":"2 Chroniques 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.23","name":"2 Chroniques 24:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.21","name":"2 Chroniques 24:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.23","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 24:23","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.024.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.024.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.24.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Quand l\u2019ann\u00e9e fut r\u00e9volue, l\u2019arm\u00e9e des Syriens monta contre Joas, et vint en Juda et \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem. Ils tu\u00e8rent parmi le peuple tous les chefs du peuple, et ils envoy\u00e8rent au roi de Damas tout leur butin.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24","name":"2 Chroniques 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.24","name":"2 Chroniques 24:24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.22","name":"2 Chroniques 24:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.24","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 24:24","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.024.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.024.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.24.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>L\u2019arm\u00e9e des Syriens arriva avec un petit nombre d\u2019hommes; et cependant l\u2019\u00c9ternel livra entre leurs mains une arm\u00e9e tr\u00e8s consid\u00e9rable, parce qu\u2019ils avaient abandonn\u00e9 l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu de leurs p\u00e8res. Et les Syriens firent justice de Joas.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24","name":"2 Chroniques 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.25","name":"2 Chroniques 24:25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.23","name":"2 Chroniques 24:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.25","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 24:25","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.024.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.024.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.24.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Lorsqu\u2019ils se furent \u00e9loign\u00e9s de lui, apr\u00e8s l\u2019avoir laiss\u00e9 dans de grandes souffrances, ses serviteurs conspir\u00e8rent contre lui \u00e0 cause du sang des fils du sacrificateur Jehojada; ils le tu\u00e8rent sur son lit, et il mourut. On l\u2019enterra dans la ville de David, mais on ne l\u2019enterra pas dans les s\u00e9pulcres des rois.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24","name":"2 Chroniques 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.26","name":"2 Chroniques 24:26","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.24","name":"2 Chroniques 24:24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.26","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 24:26","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.024.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.024.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.24.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Voici ceux qui conspir\u00e8rent contre lui: Zabad, fils de Schimeath, femme Ammonite, et Jozabad, fils de Schimrith, femme Moabite.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24","name":"2 Chroniques 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.27","name":"2 Chroniques 24:27","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.25","name":"2 Chroniques 24:25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.27","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 24:27","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.024.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.025.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.24.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>Pour ce qui concerne ses fils, le grand nombre de proph\u00e9ties dont il fut l\u2019objet, et les r\u00e9parations faites \u00e0 la maison de Dieu, cela est \u00e9crit dans les m\u00e9moires sur le livre des rois. Amatsia, son fils, r\u00e9gna \u00e0 sa place.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24","name":"2 Chroniques 24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.25.1","name":"2 Chroniques 25:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.25.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.24.26","name":"2 Chroniques 24:26","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.24.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fc3ac7466.49664016');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc3ac7466.49664016\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fc3ac7466.49664016","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fc3ac7466.49664016'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc3ac7466.49664016\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}